00:00:04.870 --> 00:00:06.700
NARRATOR: Talk about
counting sheep.

00:00:06.700 --> 00:00:09.060
There must be hundreds
of them on this hill.

00:00:09.060 --> 00:00:11.810
And this black dog,
standing front and center,

00:00:11.810 --> 00:00:13.370
driving the herd.

00:00:13.370 --> 00:00:17.420
And the most amazing thing about
this image is the perspective.

00:00:17.420 --> 00:00:19.785
Just how do you capture
a moment like this?

00:00:19.785 --> 00:00:22.842
